{"tid":1632730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［內部文宣］不定時再推下 我冇嘢講 我要驗傷","createTime":"2019-10-06T20:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T11:57:03.000Z","uid":63118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cad8d7dc334ed7bdc9db7cce2ac14702155c6713","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:27:29.000Z","msg":"有鑑於近日好多手足被捕年紀都好細<br />\n好容易俾狗狗吠兩吠就嚇親 人地想佢講乜又講乜<br />\n亦好耐冇人推過內部文宣<br />\n<br />\n最緊要記得呢幾句 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我冇嘢講 <br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要驗傷<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要投訴你 呢句就免喇 講嚟都哂氣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">被咬好多時都有cam影住 <br />\n唔好等人問 自覺大叫名、身份證<br />\n可以既話 自己除低面罩 面向鏡頭 </span></span><br />\n可能冇人問 亦可能有人問完啲狗就有所警覺<br />\n要自己有sense 馬上就要做 大叫完周圍都係人 <br />\n冇可能錄唔到 <br />\n<br />\n最後Be Water 萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n以下開放補充 有咩要注意嘅請提一提各手足<br />\n溫故知新"},{"pid":"923c21f2b9ef2051b1857c56894d0536fc761b63","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:27:58.000Z","msg":"唔要再有被自殺"},{"pid":"f3cdb5cad3b7efbbe0851ddf36b44ca990a59565","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:28:20.000Z","msg":"望鏡頭 好多人會幫手搵你"},{"pid":"4d91b96def0c84969abb4a30f054206b3f6f6f5b","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:28:46.000Z","msg":"愈高調愈安全"},{"pid":"0b419110f65b2abba75dd04888f5031e9a3ff7bb","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:29:11.000Z","msg":"入左去又好 點都好<br />\n一個都不能少"},{"pid":"6b0621246c972ebc659beb03334c3b2d01ea2bff","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:29:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c636437290552ea35ebd97b7c3b1d6393a09b1e5","tid":1632730,"uid":63118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:31:18.000Z","msg":"爬山